										stroke-width="1.6"
										stroke-linecap="round"
										stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
								</svg>
							</span>
							<span>Calm, clear communication</span>
						</li>
					</ul>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
	<section id="portfolio" class="py-24 bg-bgprimary">
		<div class="content-container">
			<h2 class="text-3xl text-primary mb-16">Types of Builds</h2>

			<div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-16">
				<!-- ITEM 1 -->
				<div class="space-y-6">
					<a
						href="https://eira.digital"
						target="_blank"
						rel="noopener noreferrer"
						class="block group"
					>
						<img
							src="/ScreenE.png"
							alt="iMac mockup"
							class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:scale-105"
						/>
					</a>

					<div class="space-y-4 text-left">
						<h3 class="text-2xl text-primary">Custom</h3>
						<p class="text-primary leading-relaxed">
							Clean, sustainable websites built with intention.
							From simple branded single page sites to fully
							custom builds that reflect your work and are
							designed to last. Custom sites are a great choice
							when you want something fast, lightweight and free
							from the limits of templates or plugins. I focus on
							creating clear, calm layouts that are easy to
							navigate and simple to maintain, giving you a site
							that feels consistent, reliable and genuinely yours.
						</p>

						<details class="group">
							<summary
								class="cursor-pointer text-primary font-medium p-10"
							>
								Read build example
							</summary>

							<div class="space-y-4 mt-2">
								<p class="text-primary leading-relaxed">
									EIRA.digital was built using Astro, HTML,
									Tailwind and minimal JavaScript for the
									responsive elements. It is hosted on my
									Infomaniak platform, a provider that
									prioritises security and is powered by 100%
									renewable energy.
								</p>
								<p class="text-primary leading-relaxed">
									The beauty of a fully custom build for a
									simple showcase site like this is that it
									massively reduces maintenance compared to
									CMSs like WordPress, while giving you
									complete freedom in design. No themes. No
									lock‑in. No bloat.
								</p>
								<p class="text-primary leading-relaxed">
									Custom builds also load faster, stay more
									secure and use fewer server resources. This
									means a lighter environmental footprint and
									a smoother experience for your visitors.
									Once designed and built, the site remains
									fast, stable and reliable, looking great for
									years with minimal upkeep.
								</p>
								<a
									href="https://eira.digital"
									target="_blank"
									class="inline-block text-primary font-medium p-10 hover:underline"
								>
									Visit EIRA.digital →
								</a>
							</div>
						</details>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- ITEM 2 -->
				<div class="space-y-6">
					<a
						href="https://prestacycle.eu"
						target="_blank"
						rel="noopener noreferrer"
						class="block group"
					>
						<img
							src="/ScreenPC.png"
							alt="Shopify mockup"
							class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:scale-105"
						/>
					</a>

					<div class="space-y-2">
						<h3 class="text-2xl text-primary">Shopify</h3>
						<p class="text-primary leading-relaxed">
							Fast, mobile first Shopify stores that are easy to
							run, simple to update and built to support your
							business as it grows. Shopify is a great choice for
							small brands because it handles the complicated
							parts for you, like hosting, security and checkout,
							while giving you a clean place to manage your
							products and orders. My approach focuses on keeping
							everything organised, lightweight and easy to
							maintain so your store stays fast and reliable
							without extra work.
						</p>

						<details class="group">
							<summary
								class="cursor-pointer text-primary p-10 font-medium mb-2"
							>
								Read build example
							</summary>

							<div class="space-y-4 mt-2">
								<p class="text-primary leading-relaxed">
									Prestacycle.eu was built as part of a full
									redesign and expansion of the Prestacycle US
									store. I created a new visual system,
									refreshed the layout and improved the
									overall structure of the theme. Once the new
									design was complete, I redeployed it across
									the EU, UK and US stores to bring
									consistency, clarity and a more modern feel
									to the brand.
								</p>
								<p class="text-primary leading-relaxed">
									The build uses metaobjects, metafields and
									custom code to make the theme more
									sophisticated and far easier to manage.
									Product data is structured cleanly, content
									is reusable and updates can be made quickly
									without touching the theme files. This keeps
									the store flexible as the catalogue grows
									and ensures the team can manage everything
									with confidence.
								</p>
								<p class="text-primary leading-relaxed">
									Shopify is an excellent choice for online
									stores and multi‑region brands like
									Prestacycle. It provides secure hosting,
									reliable checkout, fast global delivery of
									assets and a stable foundation that scales
									without extra maintenance. Once set up, the
									store remains fast, dependable and easy to
									run, giving the business more time to focus
									on products and customers rather than
									technical upkeep.
								</p>
								<a
									href="https://prestacycle.eu"
									target="_blank"
									class="inline-block text-primary p-10 font-medium hover:underline"
								>
									Visit Prestacycle.eu →
								</a>
							</div>
						</details>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- ITEM 3 -->
				<div class="space-y-6">
					<a
						href="https://ostaratherapy.co.uk"
						target="_blank"
						rel="noopener noreferrer"
						class="block group"
					>
						<img
							src="/ScreenOT.png"
							alt="WordPress mockup"
							class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:scale-105"
						/>
					</a>

					<div class="space-y-2">
						<h3 class="text-2xl text-primary">WordPress</h3>
						<p class="text-primary leading-relaxed">
							Clean, modern WordPress builds that feel clearer,
							load smoothly and are easier to look after.
							WordPress works well when you want the freedom to
							update your own content without touching code, and
							it gives you a familiar editing experience that
							grows with your site. My approach focuses on
							simplifying themes, reducing unnecessary plugins and
							creating a layout that feels calm and consistent, so
							your site stays reliable and easy to manage over
							time.
						</p>
						<details class="group">
							<summary
								class="cursor-pointer text-primary p-10 font-medium mb-2"
							>
								Read build example
							</summary>

							<div class="space-y-4 mt-2">
								<p class="text-primary leading-relaxed">
									Ostaratherapy.co.uk was a full redesign.
									Hannah wanted a clearer layout, a more
									aesthetic design and a sense of consistency
									across every page. I rebuilt the site with a
									calmer visual language, improved spacing and
									typography, and a structure that feels more
									intuitive for visitors. The aim was to
									create a space that reflects her practice
									and feels welcoming from the first click.
								</p>

								<p class="text-primary leading-relaxed">
									The build focused on simplifying the theme,
									reducing unnecessary plugins and improving
									the overall flow of the site. Content was
									reorganised so it is easier for Hannah to
									update, and the design now feels cohesive
									across her pages. I also set up flexible
									user access, so she can update as much or as
									little as she wants without worrying about
									breaking anything. Everything is designed to
									be manageable without technical knowledge.
								</p>

								<p class="text-primary leading-relaxed">
									WordPress works well when you want the
									freedom to edit your own content while still
									having a stable, secure foundation. These
									builds are hosted on Infomaniak, which means
									renewable energy, strong security and
									reliable performance. With a clean theme and
									a clear structure, the site stays fast,
									consistent and simple to maintain, giving
									Hannah the choice to manage it herself or
									let me handle it for her.
								</p>
								<a
									href="https://ostaratherapy.co.uk"
									target="_blank"
									class="inline-block text-primary font-medium p-10 hover:underline"
								>
									Visit Ostaratherapy.co.uk →
								</a>
							</div>
						</details>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="bg-bgsecondary py-20">
		<div class="content-container grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
			<!-- TEXT FIRST -->
			<div class="space-y-6">
				<h2
					class="text-secondary text-[24px] sm:text-[28px] md:text-[32px] lg:text-[36px] font-heading"
				>
					About me
				</h2>

				<p class="text-secondary leading-relaxed">
					I'm a web developer from South West Wales with a first-class
					BSc in Computing and Design, now based in the French Alps.
					My work blends technical precision with a love of clean,
					natural aesthetics; shaped by the landscapes I live and play
					in.
				</p>

				<p class="text-secondary leading-relaxed">
					Away from the screen, you'll usually find me skiing,
					climbing, or biking through the mountains. I aim to build
					websites that feel grounded, human, and quietly confident.
					Crafted to be intuitive, enduring, and a pleasure to use.
				</p>

				<p class="text-secondary leading-relaxed">
					I design for people, not just screens.
				</p>
			</div>

			<!-- IMAGE SECOND — LANDSCAPE RATIO -->
			<div class="flex justify-center md:justify-end">
				<div
					class="w-full max-w-[600px] aspect-[3/2] overflow-hidden rounded-lg shadow-md"
				>
					<img
						src="/IMG_6878.jpg"
						alt="Eva Marshall"
						class="w-full h-full object-cover object-bottom"
					/>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="content-container space-y-12 mt-20">
			<h2 class="text-3xl text-secondary mt-10 text-center">Contact</h2>
			<div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-12 text-center">
				<div class="space-y-3">
					<a
						href="tel:+33 6 12 34 56 78"
						class="text-2xl text-secondary"
					>
						+33 6 76 33 59 85
					</a>
				</div>

				<div class="space-y-3">
					<a
						href="mailto:eva@eira.digital"
						class="text-2xl text-secondary"
					>
						eva&#64;eira&#46;digital
					</a>
				</div>

				<div class="space-y-3">
					<a
						href="tel:+44 7918 653566"
						class="text-2xl text-secondary"
					>
						+44 7918 653566
					</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>
